column5: Bass opener! Hell yeah! Went out twice, fishing wasn't exactly super exciting either day... but a few nice fish were landed. Which totally made my weekend.   My little's bro's Largie... biggest of the weekend  My Largie
A few decent fish for the bass opener guys well done !!!! Thanks for sharing !!!!
Very nice! Good fish. The first one is a smallie I guess.
Not bad at all. Looks like a nice day too
